OL,3,CParalysed army veteran 'feels
OL,4,Cdeserted' after being denied benefits,
OL,5,Cfamily say
OL,7,FA British Army veteran feels "shocked"
OL,8,Fand "deserted" after being denied
OL,9,Fdisability benefits following an
OL,10,Faccident while working abroad.
OL,12,FMark Houghton, from West End in
OL,13,FHampshire, was left largely paralysed
OL,14,Fby the E-scotter crash in Dubai,
OL,15,Fearlier this year.
