OL,3,CParalysed army veteran 'feels
OL,4,Cdeserted' after being denied benefits,
OL,5,Cfamily say
OL,7,FHis family crowd funded to fly him
OL,8,Fhome in March and he has been
OL,9,Freceiving treatment at Salisbury
OL,10,FDistrict Hospital for multiple
OL,11,Finjuries ` including a broken neck `
OL,12,Fever since.
OL,14,FBut the fact Mr Houghton had been
OL,15,Fworking as a security contractor
OL,16,Foverseas for an extended period of
OL,17,Ftime has left him ineligible for
OL,18,Fpersonal independence payment (PIP).
