OL,3,CParalysed army veteran 'feels
OL,4,Cdeserted' after being denied benefits,
OL,5,Cfamily say
OL,7,FLawrence Houghton, Mark's son, told
OL,8,FITV News Meridian: "My father feels
OL,9,Fdeserted and for all intents and
OL,10,Fpurposes cast aside by the British
OL,11,Fgovernment.
OL,13,F"He has served his country to the
OL,14,Futmost and in the time of his need,
OL,15,Fhis country is not helping him."
OL,17,FMr Houghton's local MP, Liz Jarvis,
OL,18,Fraised his case in the House of
OL,19,FCommons, earlier this month.
