OL,3,CParalysed army veteran 'feels
OL,4,Cdeserted' after being denied benefits,
OL,5,Cfamily say
OL,7,FThe Liberal Democrat MP for Eastleigh
OL,8,Ftold ITV News Meridian: "I'm calling
OL,9,Fon the government to look at these
OL,10,Fcases and maybe rethink whether it's
OL,11,Ffair that somebody who has served
OL,12,Ftheir country for over 20 years and
OL,13,Fhas then decided to volunteer or work
OL,14,Fabroad, is then penalised for that.
OL,16,F"Even though he's been paying taxes in
OL,17,Fthe UK all this time. It just seems
OL,18,Fcompletely wrong to me that he should
OL,19,Fhave been treated so badly."
