OL,3,CParalysed army veteran 'feels
OL,4,Cdeserted' after being denied benefits,
OL,5,Cfamily say
OL,7,FThe Department for Work and Pensions
OL,8,Fthanked Mr Houghton for his military
OL,9,Fservice but insisted that eligibility
OL,10,Ffor personal independence payment is
OL,11,Fdependent on being present in the UK
OL,12,Ffor a specified period of time.
OL,14,FThe denial of PIP also blocks access
OL,15,Fto other disability benefits,
OL,16,Faccording to Lawrence Houghton.
