OL,3,CParalysed army veteran 'feels
OL,4,Cdeserted' after being denied benefits,
OL,5,Cfamily say
OL,7,F"For the family ` my sister, my mum `
OL,8,FIt's been traumatic. As if the
OL,9,Faccident wasn't bad enough, we're then
OL,10,Fhaving to fight tooth and nail for
OL,11,Fthings that by right he should be
OL,12,Fentitled to," Mark's son added.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,15,FWork and Pensions said: "We are deeply
OL,16,Fthankful for Mr Houghton's dedication
OL,17,Fto this country.
