OL,7,F"Eligibility for Personal Independence
OL,8,FPayment is dependent on being present
OL,9,Fin the UK for a specified period of
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,F"We recognise issues in the current
OL,13,Fsystem which is why we have launched a
OL,14,Fministerial review of PIP, in co-
OL,15,Fproduction with disabled people and
OL,16,Fthe organisations that represent them,
OL,17,Fto ensure it is fit and fair for the
OL,18,Ffuture."
